      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for CFD simulation must be validated and version-controlled under a documented QA plan meeting MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 was used under a documented software QA plan including version control, regression testing, and audit trail. All QA records available and reviewed by the credibility assessment team."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
