      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through method of manufactured solutions or equivalent benchmark problems.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has been verified against ASME benchmark problems for incompressible turbulent flow. Published verification reports confirm correct implementation of the RANS equations and scalar transport used in the hemolysis model."
    },
    {
