      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence study must demonstrate discretization error below 5% for hemolysis index QOI across at least three mesh refinement levels.",
      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation performed on three mesh levels (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.2M elements). Grid convergence index for relative hemolysis index was 3.2%, satisfying the 5% acceptance criterion. Medium mesh (5.8M) selected for production runs."
