      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental data covers all 5 operating points (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Test conditions documented with fluid temperature ±0.5°C, flow rate ±2%, and rotational speed ±10 RPM. Conditions match CFD boundary conditions within stated uncertainties."
