      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted hemolysis index must agree with experimental measurements within combined simulation and experimental uncertainty at all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) predictions agree with experimental measurements within combined uncertainty at all 5 operating points. Mean absolute error is 8.4% against experimental NIH values; relative hemolysis index RH < 1 confirmed for the device under test versus predicate. Exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
