      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index RH is the primary decision QOI. Validation uses NIH which is the experimental analog to the CFD-predicted hemolysis scalar. The mapping between NIH and RH is established through the Giersiepen power-law model, providing direct relevance to the COU decision."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
