      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry which is the reference geometry for this COU. Operating conditions span the full COU envelope. Fluid properties (bovine blood, 37°C) are representative of CPB use. Validation activities are directly relevant to the COU."
